title: Masked Special Forces
description:
Masked Special Forces is a multiplayer first-person shooter game with a myriad of customization options.  The game puts you in the shoes of a commander in the battle arena.  As a talented warrior, team up, strategize, and take down the opponents one by one. Â 
Access to an array of upgradable weapons, armory, kill messages, and victory dances on the main menu.
